夹逼定理
</h2><h4 id="1-数列型">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#1-%e6%95%b0%e5%88%97%e5%9e%8b"></a>
1. 数列型
</h4><p><img src="/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6/2.%E6%95%B0%E5%88%97%E7%9A%84%E6%9E%81%E9%99%90/image-20260702200517681.png" alt="image-20260702200517681"></p>
<p>找分母里的非主导项, 以此统一分母又不影响结果</p>
<ul>
<li>上界: 其最小</li>
<li>下界: 其最大</li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
$$
> \lim_{n \to \infty} \left( \frac{1}{n^2+1} + \frac{2}{n^2+2} + \dots + \frac{n}{n^2+n} \right)
> $$<p>上界:
</p>
$$
> \begin{align*}
> \lim_{n \to \infty} \left( \frac{1}{n^2+1} + \frac{2}{n^2+1} + \dots + \frac{n}{n^2+1} \right)
> &= \lim_{n \to \infty} \frac{1+2+\dots+n}{n^2+1} \\
> &= \lim_{n \to \infty} \frac{\dfrac{n(1+n)}{2}}{n^2+1} \\
> &= \lim_{n \to \infty} \frac{n+n^2}{2n^2+2} \\
> &= ... = \frac{1}{2}
> \end{align*}
> $$<p>
下界:
